preference.name: TC_ownership_export
preference.preference_description: Prevents a user from transferring site ownership by disabling the Transfer Ownership button in the Import/Export Options dialog box. User scope instance of this preference is a behind-the-scenes preference that is created when a user selects various import/export commands; it is used internally by the system and should not be modified. Accepts the value FALSE. If set to any other value, the system ignores the preference setting.
